<Fragment slot="intro">
<p>We repair LG dryers across Studio City — same-day in most cases, typically a 1–2 hour response, and $280–380 for the common fixes. The calls split by geography: the Valley-floor homes below Ventura Boulevard bring no-heat thermal-fuse jobs from old vent runs, while the hillside homes above Mulholland bring premium-model mechanical wear. Our LG Dryer Repair techs diagnose before they quote — call (323) 990-7550.</p>
<p>Studio City sits at the fulcrum between the Hollywood Hills and the San Fernando Valley — and the service calls here reflect that geography precisely. Above Mulholland Drive it's premium hillside homes in Fryman Canyon and Wrightwood Estates with custom laundry rooms and LG Signature machines. Below Ventura Boulevard it's Valley floor post-war bungalows and apartment buildings where the vent runs haven't been touched since the Eisenhower administration. CBS Studio Center is on Radford Avenue in the heart of the city. Universal Studios is one mile north. "I have a call time tomorrow morning" is a sentence we hear on Studio City calls the same way we hear it in Burbank — and the answer is always the same: we'll be there today.</p>
