<p><strong>Lint sensor cleaning and replacement.</strong> Fabric softener buildup on sensor bar — common in Toluca Lake border homes with heavy softener use. Cleaning free on-site. Sensor replacement $150–200.</p>

<p><strong>Door latch on DLGX4001 and DLEX3001 ($150–180).</strong> Door appears closed, dryer won't start. Safety switch not engaging. We test with multimeter first. 30–40 minutes on-site.</p>

<p><strong>Drum rollers ($280–350) and belt ($260–320).</strong> Hillside premium homes and Toluca Lake border machines 7–12 years old. We replace all four rollers plus idler pulley when accessing the drum.</p>

<p><strong>Stacked unit access — Ventura corridor apartments.</strong> Routine. 30–45 minutes, no surcharge. Foil transition replaced every time.</p>

